qIriQ nwvw jy iqsu Bwvw ivxu Bwxy ik nwie krI ]
jykr mYN ausnUM cMgw l`g jwvW qW iehI myrw Drm AsQwn qy nHhwauxw hY[ ausnUM cMgw l`gx dy ibnw ieSnwn dw kI lwB hY?
If I am pleasing to Him, then that is my pilgrimage and cleansing bath. Without pleasing Him, what good are ritual cleansings?
qIriQ = qIrQ au~qy[ nwvw = mYN ieSnwn krW[ iqsu = aus r`b nUM[ Bwvw = mYN cMgw l`gW[ ivxu Bwxy = r`b nUM cMgw l`gx qoN ibnw, jy r`b dI nzr ivc kbUl nw hoieAw[ ik nwie krI = nHwie ky mYN kIh krW?
mYN qIrQ au~qy jw ky qd ieSnwn krW jy ieauN krn nwl aus prmwqmw nUM ^uS kr skW, pr jy ies qrHW prmwqmw ^uS nhIN huMdw, qW mYN (qIrQ au~qy) ieSnwn krky kIh K`tWgw?

jyqI isriT aupweI vyKw ivxu krmw ik imlY leI ]
smUh swjy hoey jIvW nUM ijhVy mYN qkdw hW, SuB AmlW bwJoN aunHhW nUM kI imldw hY, Aqy auh kI lYNdy hn?
I gaze upon all the created beings: without the karma of good actions, what are they given to receive?
jyqI = ijqnI[ isrTI = isRStI, dunIAw[ aupweI = pYdw kIqI hoeI[ vyKw = mYN vyKdw hW[ ivxu krmw = pRBU dI myhr qoN ibnw; ijvyN: 'ivxu krmw ikCu pweIAY nwhI, jy bhu qyrw DwvY'[ (iqlMgu mhlw 1)[ ik imlY = kIh imldw hY? kuJ nhIN imldw[ ik leI = kIh koeI lY skdw hY?
Akwl purK dI pYdw kIqI hoeI ijqnI BI dunIAw mYN vyKdw hW, (ies iv`c) prmwqmw dI ikrpw qoN ibnw iksy nUM kuJ nhIN imldw, koeI kuJ nhIN lY skdw[

miq ivic rqn jvwhr mwixk jy iek gur kI isK suxI ]
mn AMdr hIry jvwhr qy lwl hn, jykr qUM gurW dI iek BI isiKAw srvx krky Aml kr lvyN[
Within the mind are gems, jewels and rubies, if you listen to the Guru's Teachings, even once.
miq ivic = (mnu`K dI) bu`D dy AMdr hI[ mwixk = mOqI[ iek isK = iek is`iKAw[ suxI = suxIey, suxI jwey[
jy siqgurU dI iek is`iKAw sux leI jwey, qW mnu`K dI bu`D dy AMdr rqn, jvwhr qy mOqI (aupj pYNdy hn, Bwv, prmwqmw dy gux pYdw ho jWdy hn)[

gurw iek dyih buJweI ]
gurU ny mYnUM iek gl smJw idqI hY[
The Guru has given me this one understanding:
xxx
(qW qy) hy siqgurU! (myrI qyry A`gy ieh Ardws hY ik) mYnUM iek ieh smJ dyh,

sBnw jIAw kw ieku dwqw so mY ivsir n jweI ]6]
smUh jIvW dw kyvl iek dwqwr hY[ auh mYnUM kdy BI nW Bu`ly[
there is only the One, the Giver of all souls. May I never forget Him! ||6||
